  "name": "Fogs Of Fear",
  "type": "spell",
  "_id": "N5DFpZbrduTlwntn",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Clans/Shi%20Usagi.jpg",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span style=\"font-family:BookInsanityRemake\">You release a dense fog from your last known position, a physical manifestation of your curse. Creatures inside the fog cannot see further than 10 feet ahead of them, gaining disadvantage on attacks made while inside the fog.<br style=\"box-sizing:border-box;-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family:BookInsanityRemake;font-size:12.8504px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(238, 229, 206);text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial\" />While within this fog, you can hide as a bonus action, when you do so, you have advantage on your stealth check as neither your shadow nor your outlines are visible to others. Any hostile creature inside the fog must make a Wisdom saving throw against the casters Genjutsu DC at the start of their turn. On a failure, they gain 1 rank of fear. Creatures affected by fear within the fog cannot lose ranks of fear normally and they can only remove all ranks by making a DC 15 Wisdom saving throw as an action. These restrictions apply only while within the radius of the fog.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:BookInsanityRemake\"><strong style=\"border:0px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-numeric:inherit;font-variant-east-asian:inherit;font-variant-alternates:inherit;font-variant-position:inherit;font-variant-emoji:inherit;font-weight:bold;font-stretch:inherit;font-size:12.8504px;line-height:inherit;font-family:BookInsanityRemake;font-optical-sizing:inherit;font-size-adjust:inherit;font-kerning:inherit;font-feature-settings:inherit;font-variation-settings:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;margin:0px;padding:0px;box-sizing:border-box;-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;letter-spacing:-0.02em;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);orphans:2;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(238, 229, 206);text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial\">At Higher Ranks:</strong> For each rank above D-Rank that you cast this jutsu, the chakra cost increases by 4, and radius increases by 5 ft and the saving throw DC to remove all ranks of fear increases by 2.</span></p>",
